Habitat &amp; Ecology - At low elevations to 
<quantity id="E99C678DE17C2CA97852282BC583D10E" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="18" pageNumber="297" unit="m" value="1500.0">
